1973:             // We should have ignored the 'ref' on the parameter while determining the applicability of argument for the given method call.
1974:             // As per Devdiv Bug #696573: '[Interop] Com omit ref overload resolution is incorrect', we must prefer non-ref omitted methods over ref omitted methods
1975:             // when determining the BetterFunctionMember.
